---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="About">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">About NoCodeAssets</h1>
      
      <div class="mt-6 text-gray-700 space-y-6">
        <p>
          NoCodeAssets is a curated marketplace for high-quality no-code templates, components, and automation workflows. 
          We connect creators of premium no-code assets with the businesses and individuals who need them.
        </p>
        
        <p>
          Our mission is to accelerate no-code development by providing access to professional-grade templates 
          and components that save time and improve the quality of no-code projects.
        </p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">For Creators</h2>
        
        <p>
          If you create templates, components, or automation workflows for no-code platforms like Webflow, Bubble, 
          Zapier, or others, we'd love to feature your work. Our marketplace gives you exposure to a targeted audience 
          of no-code builders looking for quality assets.
        </p>
        
        <p>
          <a href="/submit" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-500">Learn more about submitting your assets</a>
        </p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">For Builders</h2>
        
        <p>
          Building with no-code tools? Save time and improve quality by starting with professional templates and components. 
          Our curated collection ensures you're getting high-quality assets that follow best practices for your chosen platform.
        </p>
        
        <p>
          <a href="/" class="text-indigo-600 hover:text-indigo-500">Browse our collection</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>